{"tid":583496,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬列斯網上離奇宣布掛靴","createTime":"2018-03-07T04:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T11:43:48.000Z","uid":4957,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ae449ac805c10e579faab6d964bc4cd267cf8b","tid":583496,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"馬列斯於當地時間周二晚上在Facebook寫上自己即將掛靴的消息，內容未有詳細解釋原因，僅稱是與多名醫生商討後的結果，故令人起疑。他於貼交寫道：「在與眾多醫生作最後商議，我決定遠離足球。由於我球員生涯即將結束，我有些話想說。我想多謝每個人對我的支持及待我如此友善，他們向我展示了這美好的城市，你們永遠在我心中。」<br />\n馬列斯早前曾因為未能於冬季轉會窗離開李斯特城加盟曼城而不快，更因此未有向球隊報道多達10日之久。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=Td7eeswRvvpBVkGphoyX%2BQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=32c12eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n條友又想玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900aeb2e5d1366ad5b22f25f00a7baaa2975d35d","tid":583496,"uid":77861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7acaf7401611ae6f7c6e197cfcf6d86f98fdc23","tid":583496,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:03:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲先叫焦土，射落海都唔好益啲加害者"},{"pid":"c49d542c8cd1cf19bdf4db783f098974b1a9c6bb","tid":583496,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"惡過泥碼"},{"pid":"f8126b31c219f8af27911ae30d184ebde347032f","tid":583496,"uid":2126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"當自己係球王"},{"pid":"39fa34d1bc6cb11b5a5bc64faaf19277fce91629","tid":583496,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3de67af31f8258481ea16323c44376c6a5fac2c","tid":583496,"uid":110673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8126b31c219f8af27911ae30d184eb